jQuery

Ext JS

To get an element by id

$('foo');

Ext.fly('foo');

or

Ext.get('foo');

Create a div in the body.

var div = $("

foo

");
$(body).append(div);

var div = Ext.getBody().createChild({
   tag: 'div',
